  "detailed_description": "We have <strong>Shop Part</strong> and a tiny <strong>Life Part</strong>.<br><br><strong>SHOP</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Manage your shop.<br></li><li> Hire staff.<br></li><li> Order products<br></li><li> Sign deals and expand.</li></ul><strong>LIFE</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Buy apartments and decorate them.<br></li><li> Invite special guests or throw parties, where you can sell more stuff, in your house.</li></ul><br><strong>Apartments Above your shop are for sale!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/08ac7b8691154dbb468b747a46add3a2.avif?t=1744036856\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras_big/08ac7b8691154dbb468b747a46add3a2.avif?t=1744036856 width=800 height=165 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/8704feb27df4d1118adc7e6fbc7934a8.avif?t=1744036856\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras_big/8704feb27df4d1118adc7e6fbc7934a8.avif?t=1744036856 width=800 height=165 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/5c9774e25db442806ae3353cb9595da0.avif?t=1744036856\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras_big/5c9774e25db442806ae3353cb9595da0.avif?t=1744036856 width=800 height=165 /></span><br><br><strong>The Vision:</strong> Anything that taint the fun have no place here.<br><br>A shop life simulator, From owning a small room above the store to selling exclusive products as the highest rated shop, or scratch lottery tickets to try your luck to win big, Manage alone or with friends, in a complete shop simulation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/ed73bc703f3dfdf26d7eba9efe0b9646.webp?t=1744036856\" width=277 height=26 /></span><br>Buy & Sell scratch tickets and try your luck at winning those prizes<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/8b3e8356d19eccb1d1de1f5aa9dec845.poster.avif?t=1744036856\" width=700 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/8b3e8356d19eccb1d1de1f5aa9dec845.webm?t=1744036856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/8b3e8356d19eccb1d1de1f5aa9dec845.mp4?t=1744036856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/108b89458a6a676cbcfbd7721ffd44d3.webp?t=1744036856\" width=145 height=26 /></span><br>Only if you choose to remain open and go through the night. There is an special attention to the nights to have their own <i>different</i> vibe than days.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/014e415c0a0358d956505e3d9025aa3c.webp?t=1744036856\" width=165 height=26 /></span><br>Order and stock products, Hire staff, and organize your shelves for fast shopping by customers. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/ddfa2952d6e3f5eb1cd313dd3b0a494b.poster.avif?t=1744036856\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/ddfa2952d6e3f5eb1cd313dd3b0a494b.webm?t=1744036856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/ddfa2952d6e3f5eb1cd313dd3b0a494b.mp4?t=1744036856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/b76c9abf92fb07a494c11b5323621972.webp?t=1744036856\" width=83 height=26 /></span><br>You start small, you can grow big, <i>physically</i> and <i>spiritually</i>. Buy places and storage locations to increase your fame and your customers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/26ace490f949f39606ca5a4817b313a0.poster.avif?t=1744036856\" width=746 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/26ace490f949f39606ca5a4817b313a0.webm?t=1744036856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/26ace490f949f39606ca5a4817b313a0.mp4?t=1744036856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396090/extras/d02d275957610eb832058f102c7c4106.webp?t=1744036856\" width=143 height=26 /></span><br>Be on the lookout to hire the best staff members, each day the recruit page is updated with new people and a new set of skills.<br><br><br><strong>Planned features, In Priority Order:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A small and cozy room / home above the store.<br></li><li>Staff Room/s</li></ul><strong>Planned features, In no Particular Order:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Separate shops for each player in the lobby, either cozy shops running businesses or ultimate showdown to see who's the best shop that gets more customers!<br></li><li>Weather changes and their effect on your shop.</li></ul>",
